[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     25[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     26[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### What's Done Well (in Python companion)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     27[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     28[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Explicit warning against logging PHI or biometric data ("Never log PHI (patient names, MRNs, photos). Log patient_id references only, never the biometric data itself.")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     29[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Audit trail is non-negotiable and implemented via DynamoDB
